data.description: Experience the luxury of a home equipped with a water softening system and a spacious 3-car tandem garage. Marvel at the soaring ceilings and abundant natural light, enhanced by private 2nd-floor living areas. The open kitchen seamlessly connects to the casual dining, family room, and dining area, offering picturesque views of the covered outdoor living space. Retreat to the owner's suite at the back of the home, boasting dual sinks, a soaking tub, separate shower, and a generously-sized walk-in closet. Experience  a second bedroom conveniently located downstairs, providing versatility and convenience. Upstairs, discover three sizable bedrooms complemented by two shared baths, all accessible via the open railing game room. Step outside to the covered outdoor living area, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. Minutes away from 99 & 290.The community provides residents with a, fitness center, recreational center, pool, and playground. Access to Marvida & Miramesa community.
